Message Patterns
=========================


Message Types
------------------------
Command              - Invoke command on remote system
Document             - Distribute data amongst components
Event                - Notify components about an event
Request/Reply        - Two way communication


Message Channels
----------------------
Point to Point       -
Pub/Sub              -
Data Type            - Discover contents of message
Dead Letter          - Failed messages
Guaranteed Delivery  - Participans not online
Message Bus          - Coordinate with loose coupling


Notes
---------------------
Control Bus         - Start / Stop / Configure
Detour              - Reroute / Process / Debug
Wire Tap            - 


